stock camp
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a place where farm stock congregate [often on a sunny face, under a tree or around a gateway.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
